scdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=108609208968668fbe98ecf9_81193608"/><published>2025-07-03T17:07:04+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>a2daa69e09f26c487d5b7be5eeeae048</id><title>短炒大賺45%見証樓市重回致富路</title><updated>2025-07-03T21:04:43+08:00</updated><author><name>bbq323</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-03T21:04:43+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573092642"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573092642"&gt;290萬買，短短一年內售出420萬&lt;br&gt;又執求幾！&lt;br/&gt;淡L話要等沙示價！交住租等啦！歡迎之至&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31972893&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=108609208968668fbe98ecf9_81193608"/><published>2025-07-03T21:04:43+08:00</published></entry></feed>